Help on skill:     Ancestral rite
Usage duration:    0 round
Fatigue:           minimal
Skill type:        special
Affecting stat(s): strength, constitution, inner strength and skill percent
Through sacred ancestral rites, the barbarian performs a ritual send-off for
fallen enemies, honoring their warrior spirit and sending their soul to join
the ancestors. This act of respect for worthy foes draws upon ancient spirits
to bless the barbarian with renewed vitality, restoring both health and vigor
while gaining the favor of those who watch from beyond.
The ritual requires significant spiritual energy and can only be performed upon
the corpse of a slain enemy. The greater the fallen warrior, the more potent
the blessing received.
Using this skill costs one point of fury.
