Help on skill:     Brutal swiftness
Usage duration:    automatic
Skill type:        passive
Affecting stat(s): strength and skill percent
Some believe dexterity to be the sole provider of speed, but these fools
have not witnessed the primal fury of a charging rhino or the explosive
power of a striking bear. A well-trained barbarian, despite being a
towering colossus of scars and muscle, can move in short bursts with such
violent alacrity that onlookers mistake it for witchcraft when in
reality it is simply pure, unbridled strength.
Where others rely on nimble footwork and careful positioning, a barbarian
has learned to explode into motion through raw muscular power. Their massive
frame doesn't gracefully sidestep danger but erupts away from it, driven
by the same explosive force that propels an apex predator into its strike.
Each evasive movement is less a dodge and more a controlled detonation of
strength, the body launching itself clear of harm through sheer physical
might rather than agility.
This is not the measured dance of a duelist. This is the terrifying burst
of a warhorse changing direction, the sudden lunge of a great cat: brutal,
overwhelming, and devastatingly effective.
