Help on skill:     Spirit guidance
Usage duration:    random
Fatigue:           low
Skill type:        special
Affecting stat(s): constitution, skill percent, inner strength and awareness
The spirits of the wild do not merely offer strength. They offer insight,
clarity, wisdom that predates civilization itself. Through your deep
connection with the spiritual realm, you can channel collective wisdom of
nature, sharing this clarity with your allies.
When you open yourself as a conduit, spiritual energy flows through you
and into your companions. Their minds become sharper, their senses keener,
their abilities enhanced by this touch of the otherworld. They see threats
more clearly and perceive weaknesses that would otherwise remain hidden.
This is the gift of the Savage to their party: not just physical might,
but the wisdom of ancients and the clarity of spirit.
