Help on skill:     War paint
Usage duration:    random
Fatigue:           low
Skill type:        special
Affecting stat(s): constitution, wisdom, skill percent and inner strength
Ancient tribes knew what civilized warriors have forgotten: symbols have
power. Not through magic, but through connection. When you paint mystical
patterns across your face and body using sacred pigments, you connect to
primal forces: the fury of predators, the endurance of stone, the cunning
of the hunter. As paint dries upon your skin, you feel the power of your
ancestors flowing through sacred symbols.
The patterns are many, each channeling different aspects of the primal
world. Some enhance physical might or resilience, others sharpen combat
instincts or bring fortune in battle. The choice of pattern reflects your
intent: what you seek to embody in coming conflict.
