Help on skill:     War shout
Usage duration:    random
Fatigue:           low
Skill type:        special
Affecting stat(s): constitution, skill percent, leadership and inner strength
Battlefield chaos needs an anchor. Your allies need guidance, strength,
a rallying point for their courage. You provide this through the ancient
tradition of the war shout: a primal battle cry that resonates with power,
stirring the hearts of your companions and striking fear into enemies.
When you unleash your war cry, those who fight beside you feel renewed
vigor. Their strikes hit harder, their armor feels stronger, their resolve
hardens. This is battlefield leadership at its essence. Not commands, but
inspiration made manifest through raw vocal force. The act of rallying your
warriors also feeds your own fury, preparing you for carnage to come. This
is how the Warbringer leads: from the front, with strength that lifts all
who follow.
Using this skill generates three points of fury.
